textBox.richText: Kevin has been kidnapped and this blog has been hijacked! I can assure you that your favorite internet blogging sensation will be safely returned... of course, only if the following conditions are met: 1. One dozen chocolate covered strawberries 2. A ride in a spaceship 3. One billion gazillion TRILLION MILLION DOLLARS In summation, don’t expect very many blog posts until these conditions are fully met. Sincerely, The Anonymous Hacker
